<br>
Please feel free to post details about your answer (and why you chose it) below.  I'll probably run this as a news item later in the week assuming 95% of you chuckleheads don't answer option #4.<br>
<br>
- Sensei</FONT><FORM method=post action="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.processVote?topicID=4.topic"><table border=0 cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 width="55%"><tbody><tr><td><input type="radio" name="choice" value="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Yes, hands down.</FONT></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" name="choice" value="2"><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Yes, with some reservations about the future.</FONT></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" name="choice" value="3"><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>No, VI does a better job.</FONT></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" name="choice" value="4"><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>I didn't play EQ, but I'm one of those boobs who can't stand being excluded from anything so I'll answer anyway.</FONT></td></tr></tbody></table><P><input type=submit value="Vote"></form><a HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showMessage?topicID=4.topic&pollResults=on><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Show results</FONT></A> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uthesensei.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Sensei</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The MAN.  Damn the MAN.</span><br>  Posts: 113<br> <font color=#660000>(8/27/01 11:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sensei's 08.27.01 Poll.</span><hr size=1> Guess I should start this off.  I put &quot;Yes with some reservations.&quot;  I was disgusted with the CS policies that Verant used when I played EQ, which I got to see as a player, a webmaster and a Guide.  I've noticed so far the the 'Com has dealt with problems in a way I would never have expected Verant to deal with.<br>
<br>
Then again, the 'Com is guilty of releasing a pretty buggy game and one thing that disturbs me is the tendency to nerf (which is going to happen, and sometimes should) but do so BEFORE other issues are dealt with.  Personally I'd rather see a focus on game-stability issues and exploits before minor class tweaks and balance issues (unless a class is bugged, like the MA's).<br>
<br>
A good example of this is the surgery nerf in 12.52.  Previously you could click multiple times on this to boost your treatment skill +100 each time, allowing a player to put in implants that were vastly higher than what they arguably should be allowed to obtain.  The concept fix for this is that a doctor or class with a higher treatment skill would be able to use an item to transfer some treatment skill points to the target ... however this feature is busted still, and the surgery machine nerf went in anyways.<br>
<br>
Verant did this to us constantly as monks and with other classes as well -- nerf, THEN support, rather than the other way around.  I've always thought it was an utterly piss-poor way of dealing with balance issues and does nothing but alienate the playerbase.<br>
<br>
All in all, though, I think Funcom is on the right track, and assuming they stay the course they are on (and brush up a tad on oeffectively communicating with us) I think (and hope) good things will come, because AO really is a great game.<br>
<br>
My 2 credz,<br>
<br>
- Sensei <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ugrimlakin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimlakin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 163<br> <font color=#660000>(8/27/01 11:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sensei's 08.27.01 Poll.</span><hr size=1> I voted yes hands down....<br>
